description: Meet Aaron Skyline, a 19 year old semi pro mixed martial arts fighter. Instead of throwing him immediately to the sharks by pairing him with TommyD or Mason Wyler, we decided to take it easy on the young man and give him a NextDoorMale scene to get him up to speed. You may not know it, but being naked in front of a camera doesn't always come naturally. Luckily for us, this kid wasn't fazed one bit.Enjoy!
title: Aaron Skyline
